              "text": "In Nasr's view, Khamenei is an \"unusual sort of dictator\"."
            },
            {
              "text": "Officials under Khamenei influence the country's various powerful, and sometimes bickering, institutions, including \"the parliament, the presidency, the judiciary, the Revolutionary Guards, the military, the intelligence services, the police agencies, the clerical elite, the Friday prayer leaders and much of the media\", as well as various \"nongovernmental foundations, organizations, councils, seminaries and business groups\"."
            }
          ]
